2,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T09:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1名年輕OL下班後到按摩店找梁姓按摩師做全身舒壓，在按摩的過程<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中還</span></span>因為太舒服而睡著了，在半夢半醒之間，她覺得下面怪怪的，於是睜開眼睛一看，赫然發現按摩師沒穿褲子正跨跪在她的小腿兩側，整個頭埋在她兩腿間並舔她的下體，準備欺侮她，她嚇得用腳狠踹按摩師的下體並大聲呼救，台北地檢署調查後，依強制性交未遂罪，將這名色按摩師起訴。<br />\n檢警查出，這名20多歲的粉領上班族，今年3月12日凌晨3點左右，與好友陳姓女子一同前往台北市中山區一家足體按摩店進行全身按摩，2人在店家的安排下，前往4樓的2間VIP包廂，女子由1名44歲的梁姓男按摩師服務，好友陳女則由1名葉姓師父服務。<br />\n按摩的過程中，女子因為太舒服而呼呼大睡，不懷好意的梁男竟然趁機偷偷脫掉客人的內褲及自己的內外褲，然後爬上按摩床，雙腳跨跪在仰躺著女客人的小腿兩側，用舌頭舔弄女子的下體，然後還準備趁機「提槍」上陣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/08/214305_bc8f2837e87e2695a696859e2eb12511.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F08%2F214305_bc8f2837e87e2695a696859e2eb12511.png&h=e73a372c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180608/1369322\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180608%2F1369322&d=MWM9e7Lkmcv0%2FiCloJa%2BCDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=ebf677af\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180608%2F1369322&h=6cf552b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180608/1369322</a></blockquote><br />\n 扳回一仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac77cdd6c5cc26a324363c5534b2c76ba043c7e9","tid":694652,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T09:30:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"22ec5667fa7e454d87beaf66ad90293fe535a687","tid":694652,"uid":17832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T10:51:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8753a3259b55ca48f4f985dae4755b85c52fe715","tid":694652,"uid":83125,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/09/192619_d900e01da28657c068680f1dc8762f8f.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F09%2F192619_d900e01da28657c068680f1dc8762f8f.gif&d=MWM9e7Lkmcv0%2FiCloJa%2BCDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=65715638\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/09/192619_d900e01da28657c068680f1dc8762f8f.gif</a><br />\n諗起已經扯撚咗<br />\n利申青頭boy"},{"pid":"5536cc974b79e3d4f33173a646ccc4f5960b43fb","tid":694652,"uid":106036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:34:21.000Z","msg":"蘋果d圖真係好生動"},{"pid":"b5b64cdb5217d963b380178df9db69244682ef2b","tid":694652,"uid":5253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T11:58:06.000Z","msg":"不要強姦<br />\n去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b970d0181fa6c04024929731552bae9dc4eefc60","tid":694652,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:09:10.000Z","msg":"或曰台灣者"},{"pid":"6a71607276a72f32bec4639c8f58ef4596796422","tid":694652,"uid":11962,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b970d0181fa6c04024929731552bae9dc4eefc60","tid":694652,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:09:10.000Z","msg":"或曰台灣者"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:11:49.000Z","msg":"或曰︰「台灣者，盪女痴男滿盈。其人好譏香港為支那，不然，則思淫亂。惑人妻、亂人夫，刁風月，弄牆隙、交合行淫，行淫交合，迷姦強暴，強暴迷姦，不絕於城也。堂姊、表妹、兄嫂、內娣、朋女、友孫、皆可慾淫。弱女信徒，秘書病人，或其親朋子侄，無一倖免。女盜口穴逢迎，奪夥計貞操。師者巨乳貶壓，誘學子心性。亦不然，交合時暗錄活春宮，分別時皇皇然脅之，又得幾回歡愉。女甫口角，輒奔舊愛，哭啼哭啼，又變嘿咻嘿咻。男欲內發，女言不可，搖頭嗔目，元陽閉穴。」此之謂也。"},{"pid":"1118eff13459e4040f1bb6fcd7a87c4fd14b7b95","tid":694652,"uid":97551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"好撚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}